msgctxt "header"
msgid "Thanks for taking action. Can you do 2 more things?"
msgstr "Merci d’avoir soutenu notre action. Nous avons encore 2 (petites) choses à vous demander."

msgctxt "body"
msgid ""
"Thank you for saying that you support net neutrality. We have two more things to ask you to do.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"First, if you've never received emails from Mozilla before, look in your email in a few minutes for a message. If you want to receive updates on this campaign and others, you must click the link in your inbox to opt-in for emails.\r\n"
"\r\n"
"Second, can you add a donation to Mozilla to help us bring back net neutrality? Most people give around $28 USD, and your contribution will support our work to reclaim the internet from big tech."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "donate_text"
msgid "Yes, I'll chip in"
msgstr "Oui, je participe"

msgctxt "dismiss_text"
msgid "No thanks"
msgstr "Non merci"
